  "title": "docs: add guidelines for widget and common tests",
  "body": "**Summary**\r\n\r\nThis PR adds a section on the contributing guidelines, documenting how to write tests for InstantSearch widgets.\r\n\r\nIn addition, it adds a common test suite for Breadcrumb's base behavior as an example that contributors can use for their own needs.\r\n\r\nFX-2066\r\n\r\n> **Note**\r\n> Because this PR has 2 scopes, instead of squashing, after review I can rewrite the history to keep scoped commits and merge both of them into the main branch.",
